    <string name="ayuda">Help</string>
    <string name="ayudadescripcion">
        Welcome to Drive Smart.
        \n\nThis app will allow you to know the best route according to your preferences. It will also
        give you on-site information on any possible incident on your route.

        \n\nTo start with, I recommend that you go to Settings, choose your preferred language, route
        options and type of information pop-ups you want to see while you are driving. After that,
        press “Select new route” and choose the origin and destination of your route.

        \n\nOnce you see the route on the screen, you will be able to navigate through the map and see
        the layout of your route. You can also check any incidents by pressing “Get incidents”.
        If you press on an incident, you will see detailed information about it.

        \n\nYour route will be saved in the app for future use and information about the actual duration
        of your trip and its estimated travel time.

        \n\nThank you for using Drive Smart and have a nice trip!
    </string>


